          "reviewBody": "I don't have option to select negative star .\nWorst school I have ever seen. Fees is very high but standard of teaching is very low. Teachers resigned from school frequently. Mindset of school management is to earn money only. They sell books and copy from school at very higher prices and they don't provide any bills. They also sell uniform of both seasons in school at very high prices which cost around 4 to 5 K here also they don't provide any permanent bill. School is involved in illegal practise by tax evasion . They hide taxes from government by not providing permanent bill.\nTeachers are care less . If you missed fees due to any personal reasons school management dosen't care and don't allow child to appear in examinations.\nIf the moto of school management is money minded and how involve in tax evasion. Then we can understand what they will teach our childs.\nDon't think about this school. If you have huge money to waste you can go with this school.",
